title: Hour 1 - Jeremy Pruitt (07-01-20)

description:
Tennessee Head FB Coach Jeremy Pruitt tells Dan that they have not had any positive covid-19 test from any of their players. Coach says that the players will get to go away for 3 days and they will start all over again with the testing once they return.
